<H2>Privacy Policy Chart - Online Service Providers</H2>
<BR>
This Privacy Policy Chart details the fair information practices of major commercial online service providers.  We arrived at these results by analyzing the service providers' written polices (such as Terms of Service) and policies distributed online to subscribers.  
<P>
Boxes marked <STRONG>Yes</STRONG> indicate that the service provider practices this fair information policy, and that the practice is disclosed to members.  Boxes marked <STRONG>No</STRONG> indicate that the service provider does not practice this fair information policy.  Boxes marked <STRONG>NP</STRONG>, or &quot;No Policy&quot;, indicate that no policy statement is available that informs the subscriber of this fair information practice.  Boxes marked <STRONG>n/a</STRONG>, or &quot;not applicable&quot;, indicate that the specific fair information practice does not apply to this commercial online service provider.
