	</TR>
	<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
		<TH>11. Can you see the <A HREF="../terms.html#subscription">subscription information</A> the service maintains about you? <A HREF="terms.html#access">(Access)</A></TH><TD><A HREF="AOL/AOL.html#tos2">Yes</A></TD><TD><a href="CompuServe/CompuServe.html#go_member">Yes</a></TD><TD><a href="MSN/MSN.html#one_five">Yes</a></TD><TD><a href="Prodigy/P_excerpts.html">Yes</a></TD>
	</TR>
	<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
		<TH>12. Can you correct and update <A HREF="../terms.html#subscription">subscription information</A>? <A HREF="terms.html#correction">(Correction)</A></TH><TD><A HREF="AOL/AOL.html#tos2">Yes</A></TD><TD><A HREF="CompuServe/CompuServe.html#go_member">Yes</A></TD><TD><a href="MSN/MSN.html#one_five">Yes</a></TD><TD><a href="Prodigy/P_excerpts.html">Yes</a></TD>
	</TR>
	<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
		<TH>13. Can you see the <A HREF="../terms.html#person_id">personally identifiable transactional information</A> the service maintains about you? <A HREF="../terms.html#access">(Access)</A></TH><TD>NP</TD><TD>No</TD><TD><a href="MSN/MSN.html#one_five">Yes</a></TD><TD>NP</TD>
	</TR>
	<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
		<TH>14. Can you correct and update <A HREF="../terms.html#person_id">personally identifiable transactional information</A>? <A HREF="../terms.html#correction">(Correction)</A></TH><TD>NP</TD><TD>No</TD><TD><a href="MSN/MSN.html#one_five">Yes</a></TD><TD>NP</TD>
	</TR>
	<TR>
		<TH>Fair Information Principle / <I><A HREF="../terms.html#online">Commerical Online Service</A></I></TH>
