	</TR>
	<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
		<TH>15. Is your name and email address automatically made available in a directory to other subscribers?</TH><TD><A HREF="AOL/AOL_memdirect.html">No</A></TD><TD><a href="CompuServe/CompuServe.html#mail_policy">No</a></TD><TD>NP</TD><TD><A HREF="Prodigy/P_excerpts.html#priv_policy">No</A></TD>
	</TR>
	<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
