<H2>Internet White Pages: Are you listed?</H2>
There are a number of Internet sites that contain databases of names and
e-mail address of many Internet users.  Check these directories to see if
you are listed.
<UL>
<LI><STRONG><A HREF="http://bigfoot.com/">Bigfoot</A></STRONG>
<LI><STRONG><A HREF="http://www.esp.co.uk/">ESP</A></STRONG>
<LI><STRONG><A HREF="http://www.four11.com/">Four11 Directory Services</A></STRONG>
<LI><STRONG><A HREF="http://www.iaf.net/">Internet Address Finder</A></STRONG>
<LI><STRONG><A HREF="http://www.lookup.com/">LookUP!</A></STRONG>
<LI><STRONG><A HREF="http://okra.ucr.edu/okra/">Okra net.citizen Directory
Service</A></STRONG>
<LI><STRONG><A HREF="http://www.whowhere.com/">WhoWhere? White Pages</A></STRONG>
