CDT POLICY POST 4/11/95                                      Number 9

CONTENTS: (1) House CDA Sponsor Calls for Hearings, Go-Slow Approach
          (2) Text of Rep. Tim Johnson's Letter to Chairman Fields
          (3) About the Center For Democracy and Technology

