LAW J. 733 (1964), &quot;Beyond the New Property,&quot; 56 BROOK. L.R. 731
(1990); &quot;The Liberty Impact of the New Property,&quot; 31 WM. &amp;
MARY L. REV. 295 (1990).<A NAME="ft_5"></A><BR>
