    Citizens Internet Empowerment Coalition Trial Update No. 6
              Afternoon Update -  March 22, 1996 1:00 pm ET
  -----------------------------------------------------------------
                     http://www.cdt.org/ciec/
                        ciec-info@cdt.org
  -----------------------------------------------------------------
   CIEC UPDATES intended for members of the Citizens Internet
