    23           I would use the question.

    24                    And I think -- 

    25                    JUDGE SLOVITER:  Go ahead.


                    


                                                                            34

     1                    MR. HANSEN:  I think there is some notion to the

     2           fact that the Government, the Congress can draw some lines in

